<L>__{exterior courtyard dancers}
<A>__{older chicano couples dance to mexican music playing from speakers set up in the apartment complex courtyard. we tilt up to see enrique watching from his window }
<L>__{interior apartment night}
<A>__{music still blasting. enrique steps away from the window, and sits on the bed of his drab furnished apartment. he goes back to tying knots in a length of clothesline splicing it to another. on the bed beside him are new flashlights and the batteries, still in their packaging. he begins to coil the rope it is hundreds of feet long.}
